text:
You can get something that behaves more like a dictionary using

c = Gen.nested_view(get_choices(trace))

and call keys on that! Note that if you have hierarchical addresses this will behave like a nested dictionary — you may need to do c[:a][:b] to grab an inner choice, or keys(c[:a]) to get all the inner choices under :a.
